# Deploying Wazuh 4.14.6

This guide documents how I deployed **Wazuh 4.14.6** on **Ubuntu Server 24.04.4 LTS** as the Security Information and Event Management (SIEM) platform for my SOC Automation project.

Instead of reproducing the official installation guide, I followed the Wazuh documentation and focused this guide on verifying the deployment, configuring the environment, and integrating Wazuh with the remaining SOC components.

