# Install the Windows Agent

After deploying the manager, I installed the Wazuh Agent on the Windows 10 endpoint and connected it to the Wazuh Manager.

This enabled endpoint telemetry to be forwarded into the SIEM.

---

# Install Sysmon

To improve endpoint visibility, Microsoft Sysmon was installed on the Windows endpoint.

Sysmon provides detailed logging for:

- Process Creation
- Network Connections
- Driver Loading
- Registry Events
- File Creation

---

